author: Oliver JJ Lane
title: Populist Outsider Geert Wilders in Combative Mood as the Netherlands Prepares to Go to the Polls
text: The traditionally liberal Netherlands will go to the polls Wednesday morning to select new members of parliament and perhaps a new government, and anti-mass migration, Eurosceptic Geert Wilders is fighting to come out on top in a contest which has seen his ratings dented in recent weeks.
